To watch for changes in you scss and compile in real time, use: sass --watch src/css:main/css

Put your application's scss styles in src/css/partials/_common.scss

Include any other partials in src/css/style.scss, like so:

/* Some HTML 5 Boilerplate stuff */
@import "partials/boilerplate-top";
/* Put your styles in partials/_common.scss */
@import "partials/common";
/* @import "partials/my-super-special-mixin" */
/* Some more HTML 5 Boilerplate stuff */
@import "partials/boilerplate-bottom"; 